node.title: Barstool Cookie Review - My Mom's Cookies (Special Guest My Dad)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dave Portnoy on August 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'JIMMYHAYES JIMMY HAYES 1989 2021 UeR'.

node.text: Rip Jimmy Hayes. Easily one the funniest, most genuine guys I’ve been lucky enough to meet in 2 decades of doing Barstool.  There are very few people that everybody likes.  Jimmy was 1 of them.  A tragic reminder how fragile life can be and to live life  to the fullest cause you never know what tomorrow can bring.
